<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>13319</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>16318</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿拉丁太开心了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>16319</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23496</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他终于和美丽的公主结婚，并且住在辉煌的宫殿里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23497</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28176</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿拉丁早已经忘记了邪恶的魔法师。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28177</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34760</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是朋友们，马格里布可没忘记那盏神灯。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34761</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40237</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>噢，马格里布从来没停止想过它。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40238</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48321</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他用咒语制作了一个蓝色的水晶球，通过它可以找到任何东西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48322</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53104</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他希望通过球里的迷雾来找到神灯。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53105</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61055</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“噢，我在水晶球里可以看见宝库！”他边说边盯着球，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61056</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65179</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯，但是灯在哪里？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65180</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70168</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他围着水晶球转，希望看得更清楚些。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70169</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75023</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我看不见那盏灯，也看不见那个男孩儿，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75024</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79189</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他可能已经躺在哪个地方死了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79190</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88369</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>马格里布在房间里走来走去，然后把干瘦的手放在水晶球上边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88370</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98238</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“告诉我阿拉丁在哪里！”魔法师命令道。他又看向那团雾。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98239</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101809</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是什么？”他小声说道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101810</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107545</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的脸变黑了，苍白的眼睛发出了亮光。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107546</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114259</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>马格里布看见阿拉丁在一座宫殿里，而没有死在宝库里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114260</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119734</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他穿着体面，正在和一位美丽的女人散步。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119735</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126120</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他还活着。”马格里布大叫，“他还很富有！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126121</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132534</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他又看向水晶球：“而且他还娶了公主！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132535</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139414</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那一天，太阳下山以前，魔法师启程前往阿拉丁的家。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139415</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146574</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要再次找到他！”他说，“这一次，我要拿到神灯！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146575</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154874</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当马格里布到达阿拉丁所在的城市时，每个人都在讨论阿拉丁的宫殿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154875</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162030</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“它比国王的宫殿还要大。”一个男人说，“你看到就知道了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162031</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167328</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是神灯的魔力！”马格里布嘟囔道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167329</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172740</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他转身朝向那个男人：“那个宫殿在哪里？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172741</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176770</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那个男人指向一条路，又说：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176771</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184625</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是阿拉丁现在不在家，他外出打猎去了，一个星期后才回来。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184626</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190013</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>邪恶的马格里布听到这儿，想出了一个计划。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190014</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195452</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天，他去买了几盏新灯。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195453</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199758</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它们看起来和神灯一模一样。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199759</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205439</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>马格里布穿得破破烂烂的，拿着灯走在街上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205440</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210797</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谁要用旧灯换新灯啊？”他喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210798</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214826</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>人们听见他的叫声之后都摇摇头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214827</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224202</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“新灯换旧灯？”一个女人大笑道，“谁听说过这么愚蠢的买卖？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224203</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232759</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>马格里布没有理会，他在街上走来走去，叫得越来越大声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232760</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237156</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谁想用旧灯换新灯啊？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237157</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>242226</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>渐渐的，他走近了阿拉丁的宫殿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>242227</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>247948</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>贝德拉公主和仆人们正在宫殿的窗户边坐着，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>247949</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>253745</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们正在边吃水果糖边用丝绸织围巾。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>253746</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260355</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那是什么声音？”贝德拉公主问道，“谁在大叫？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260356</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264069</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>其中一个仆人跑向窗户。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264070</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>269599</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谁想用旧灯换一盏新灯？”马格里布喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>269600</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>274505</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>靠近窗户的仆人大笑了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>274506</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>279861</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你在笑什么呢？”公主问道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>279862</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>287841</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是个疯子！”仆人大叫道，“他想用他的新灯来换旧灯！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>287842</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>292303</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>公主贝德拉听到后，立刻站了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>292304</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>297290</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们有一盏旧铜灯。”她说，“我去把它拿来。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>297291</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>301204</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>说着，公主跑出了房间。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>301205</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>307539</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当她回来的时候，她手里正拿着阿拉丁的神灯。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>307540</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>314535</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“给你。”她对仆人说，“把这个又脏又旧的灯拿到楼下去，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>314536</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>325584</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>看看这个男人是不是在说实话，会不会用新灯换我们的旧灯！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>